---
title: Cherry Tomato, Courgette & Cheddar Pizza with Pear & Mixed Leaf Salad
description: Add extra flavour to your vegetarian pizza by roasting the veggies first to ensure every bite is a tasty delight. Then, infuse the
sauce with garlic for a fragrant flavour so divine that you’ll never rely on takeaway again!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cherry-tomato-courgette-sage-pizza-0ab6f02b.jpg
